<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Heart-strings" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Heart-strings,</orth> the tendons supposed to brace and sustain the heart: <bibl n="shak. luc 1141" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1141</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.2.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. IV, 2, 62</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.365" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 365</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.261" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 261</bibl>. Used in the sing. by Pistol: <cit><quote>from heart-string I love the lovely bully,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.47" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 1, 47</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>